name: Garindan (V)
Lore: 'Long-nosed, male Kubaz from Kubindi. Spy. Squealed on Obi-Wan and Luke outside Docking Bay 94. Works for Jabba the Hutt or the highest bidder. Not particularly brave.',
Text: 'Adds one to the power of anything he pilots. May deploy -1 as a ''react''; shuffle any Reserve Deck. Ignores Objective deployment restrictions. Unless alone, may place Garindan in Used Pile to cancel a just drawn Weapons Destiny here. [Virtual Block 2] Imperial Domination ignores Garindan.',
